NAVIGATIONAL WARNING - ADDITIONAL NR. 8 230302 UTC DEC
WAVE HEIGHT WARNING 300CM TSS TERSCHELLING - GERMAN BIGHT
ISSUED AT 230300 UTC DEC
CONTAINER VESSELS WITH A LENGTH OF 100-200M ARE AT RISK OF
LOSING CONTAINERS DURING HEAVY SEA CONDITIONS IN
PARTICULAR FROM A WEST-NORTHWEST TO NORTHERLY DIRECTION.
THESE VESSELS SHOULD ALTER COURSE IF NECESSARY TO AVOID
COMING ABEAM TO THE WAVES AND TAKE OTHER APPROPRIATE
MEASURES TO AVOID LOSING CONTAINERS
